        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(voice-call): avoid OpenAI realtime double greeting",
        "body": "Fixes #85846\n\n## Summary\n\n- Avoid the voice-call plugin's duplicate OpenAI realtime greeting by making proactive/manual OpenAI speech an instructed `response.create` instead of injecting a synthetic user message.\n- Keep outbound OpenAI calls proactive: the bridge still calls `triggerGreeting()` on ready when an initial message exists.\n- Preserve configured session instructions for explicit/manual speech and carry the latest response intent through deferred, cancel, and active-response retry paths.\n- Keep session instructions as the base voice instructions; initial greeting instructions are scoped to the first proactive response.\n- Narrow the realtime test callback before invoking optional `sendUserMessage`, fixing the CI `check-test-types` failure that appeared on head `31c07ccee8f1ee9dc3a45c78cc35177cd09d1ed1`.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `CI=true pnpm check:test-types` -> passed on the previous refreshed head after the optional-callback test fix; current `main` now has an unrelated test-type failure outside this PR's touched surface.\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/voice-call/src/webhook/realtime-handler.test.ts extensions/openai/realtime-voice-provider.test.ts --reporter=dot` -> 2 files, 74 tests passed\n- `./node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check extensions/voice-call/src/webhook/realtime-handler.ts extensions/voice-call/src/webhook/realtime-handler.test.ts extensions/openai/realtime-voice-provider.ts extensions/openai/realtime-voice-provider.test.ts`\n- `./node_modules/.bin/oxlint --tsconfig config/tsconfig/oxlint.core.json extensions/voice-call/src/webhook/realtime-handler.ts extensions/voice-call/src/webhook/realtime-handler.test.ts extensions/openai/realtime-voice-provider.ts extensions/openai/realtime-voice-provider.test.ts`\n- `git diff --check refs/remotes/upstream-safe/main...HEAD`\n- `git diff --check`\n\nSigned head: `af3594b0fff6305cc7b01b81edd0cce280034f39`.\n\nNote: no live Twilio/OpenAI outbound call was run in this environment.",
